room_title: Escape room "Mystery Manor" by 60 to Escape in Chicago
room_address: Gurnee Mills, 6170 W Grand Ave. Gurnee, IL 60031
room_description: An eccentric family has apparently left their entire fortune (and an incredible mansion) to their only living relative... YOU. Upon arriving at the home, you realize things aren't so simple. Uncover the mysteries that surround this bizarre home and take home an immense fortune, or suffer a fate worse than death!
